\c 6
\s Umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* ulethwa eJerusalema
\p
\v 1 UDavida wabuya wabuthanisa bonke abakhethiweyo koIsrayeli, inkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu.
\v 2 UDavida wasesukuma wahamba labo bonke abantu ababelaye, besuka eBahala-Juda ukuze benyuse umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu usuka lapho, obizo lawo libizwa ngebizo leN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla\x + 1 Lan. 13.6-14.\x*, ehlala \add phakathi\add* \w kwamakherubhi\w**\x + Eks. 25.22. 1 Sam. 4.4.\x* phezu kwawo.
\v 3 Basebewukhweza umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu enqoleni entsha\x + 1 Sam. 6.7.\x*, bewukhupha endlini kaAbinadaba eyayiseqaqeni; njalo uUza loAhiyo amadodana kaAbinadaba batshayela leyonqola entsha\x + 1 Sam. 7.1,2.\x*.
\v 4 Bayikhipha-ke endlini kaAbinadaba eyayiseqaqeni kanye lomtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu, njalo uAhiyo ehamba phambi komtshokotsho.
\v 5 UDavida lendlu yonke yakoIsrayeli basebetshaya phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* ngazo zonke izinto \add zokutshaya\add* zesihlahla \w sefiri\w**, langamachacho, langezigubhu zezintambo\x + 1 Kho. 10.12.\x*, langezigujana, langamahlwayi\x + Eks. 15.20.\x*, langezinsimbi ezincencethayo\x + Hlab. 150.5.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Bathi befika esizeni sikaNakoni, uUza welulela\x + Nani 4.15. 7.9. 1 Lan. 15.2,13,15.\x* \add isandla sakhe\add* emtshokotshweni kaNkulunkulu, wawubamba, ngoba inkabi zakhubeka\x + 5.8. 1 Lan. 13.9.\x*.
\v 7 Intukuthelo yeN\nd kosi\nd* yasimvuthela uUza; uNkulunkulu wamtshaya khonapho ngenxa yalesisiphambeko; wasefela khonapho phansi komtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu\x + 1 Sam. 6.19.\x*.
\v 8 UDavida wasethukuthela ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* imfohlele uUza \add nge\add*sikhala; waseyibiza leyondawo \add ngokuthi\add* yiPerezi-Uza, kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 9 UDavida waseyesaba iN\nd kosi\nd* ngalolosuku, wathi: Umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* uzakuza njani kimi\x + 1 Kho. 17.18.\x*?
\v 10 Ngakho uDavida kavumanga ukuwudlulisela kuye umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* emzini kaDavida; kodwa uDavida wawuphambulela endlini kaObedi-Edoma umGithi\x + 4.3. Josh. 21.24,25.\x*.
\v 11 Umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* wasuhlala endlini kaObedi-Edoma umGithi inyanga ezintathu. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimbusisa uObedi-Edoma lendlu yakhe yonke\x + 1 Lan. 26.5. Gen. 30.27.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Kwasekubikelwa inkosi uDavida kwathiwa: IN\nd kosi\nd* ibusisile indlu kaObedi-Edoma lakho konke okwakhe ngenxa yomtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu. Ngakho uDavida wasehamba wenyusa umtshokotsho kaNkulunkulu ewususa endlini kaObedi-Edoma, ewusa emzini kaDavida ngentokozo\x + 1 Lan. 15.25-29. 1 Kho. 8.1.\x*.
\v 13 Kwasekusithi lapho labo abathwele umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* sebehambe izinyathelo eziyisithupha\x + Nani 4.15. Josh. 3.3. 1 Lan. 15.2,15.\x*, wahlaba inkabi lokunonisiweyo\x + 1 Kho. 8.5. 1 Lan. 15.26.\x*.
\v 14 UDavida wasegida ngamandla wonke phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Eks. 15.20. Hlab. 30.11.\x*\nd*; uDavida wayebhince \w i-efodi\w** yelembu elicolekileyo\x + 1 Sam. 2.18.\x*.
\v 15 Ngokunjalo uDavida lendlu yonke yakoIsrayeli bawenyusa umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* ngokumemeza langokukhala kophondo.
\v 16 Kwasekusithi lapho umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\nd* ungena emzini kaDavida, uMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli walunguza ngewindi, wabona inkosi uDavida eseqa egida phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*; wameyisa enhliziyweni yakhe\x + Hlu. 5.28. 2 Kho. 9.30.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Basebewungenisa umtshokotsho weN\nd kosi\x + 1 Lan. 16.1-3.\x*\nd*, bawubeka endaweni yawo\x + 1 Lan. 15.1.\x* phakathi kwethente uDavida ayelimisele wona\x + 1 Lan. 16.1.\x*; uDavida wasenikela iminikelo yokutshiswa phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd* leminikelo yokuthula\x + 1 Kho. 8.5,62,63.\x*.
\v 18 Kwathi uDavida eseqedile ukunikela iminikelo yokutshiswa leminikelo yokuthula, wabusisa abantu ebizweni leN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla\x + 1 Kho. 8.14,55.\x*.
\v 19 Wababela bonke abantu, ixuku lonke lakoIsrayeli, kusukela kwabesilisa kusiya kwabesifazana, ngulowo lalowo iqebelengwana lesinkwa, leqatha lenyama, lesinkwa sezithelo zevini ezonyisiweyo. Basebehamba abantu bonke, ngulowo lalowo emzini wakhe\x + 1 Lan. 16.43.\x*.
\p
\v 20 UDavida wasebuyela ukubusisa indlu yakhe\x + 1 Lan. 16.43.\x*. UMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli wasephuma ukuhlangabeza uDavida, wathi: Idunyiswe kangakanani inkosi yakoIsrayeli lamuhla, ezembule lamuhla phambi kwamehlo encekukazi zenceku zayo\x + 6.14,16. 1 Sam. 19.24.\x* njengomunye wabayize ezembula lokuzembula\x + Hlu. 9.4.\x*!
\v 21 UDavida wasesithi kuMikhali: Ngaphambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, eyangikhetha phambi kukayihlo laphambi kwendlu yakhe yonke, yangimisa ukuthi ngibe ngumbusi phezu kwabantu beN\nd kosi\nd*, phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + 1 Sam. 13.14. 15.28.\x*; ngakho ngizadlala phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + 6.5.\x*\nd*.
\v 22 Ngisazadeleleka-ke kakhulu kulalokhu, ngehliselwe phansi emehlweni ami; kodwa ngezincekukazi okhulume ngazo, ngizadunyiswa yizo.
\v 23 Njalo uMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli kabanga lamntwana kwaze kwaba lusuku lokufa kwakhe.
